# ğŸ•¹ï¸ GridVerse: A Multiplayer Tile-Based Chat Game

**GridVerse** is a real-time multiplayer tile-based game that enables players to move across a 2D map, interact with the environment, and engage in retro-style proximity chat when adjacent to each other.

> Built using **React**, **Tailwind CSS**, and **Go** with **WebSockets** for real-time communication and **ScyllaDB** for persistent data storage.

